sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Data Scientist
    participant JupyterWebApp as jupyter-web-app<br/>UI Service
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant NotebookCtrl as Notebook Controller<br/>NotebookReconciler
    participant CullingCtrl as Culling Controller<br/>CullingReconciler
    participant StatefulSet as StatefulSet<br/>Notebook Pod 8888/TCP
    participant IstioCP as Istio Control Plane<br/>Optional
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Collector

    %% Flow 1: Notebook Creation
    rect rgb(220, 240, 255)
        Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Notebook Creation
        User->>JupyterWebApp: Request notebook via UI
        JupyterWebApp->>K8sAPI: POST Notebook CR<br/>HTTPS Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Watch notification<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: CREATE StatefulSet<br/>HTTPS ServiceAccount Token
        NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: CREATE Service<br/>HTTPS ServiceAccount Token
        alt USE_ISTIO=true
            NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: CREATE VirtualService<br/>HTTPS ServiceAccount Token
            K8sAPI->>IstioCP: VirtualService created
        end
        NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: UPDATE Notebook status<br/>HTTPS ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>User: Notebook ready
    end

    %% Flow 2: Idle Notebook Culling
    rect rgb(255, 240, 220)
        Note over CullingCtrl,NotebookCtrl: Flow 2: Idle Notebook Culling
        CullingCtrl->>StatefulSet: GET /api/kernels<br/>HTTP/8888 Bearer Token
        StatefulSet-->>CullingCtrl: Kernel activity data<br/>HTTP Response
        CullingCtrl->>CullingCtrl: Check idle time<br/>vs CULL_IDLE_TIME
        alt Idle threshold exceeded
            CullingCtrl->>K8sAPI: ADD kubeflow-resource-stopped annotation<br/>HTTPS ServiceAccount Token
            K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Watch notification
            NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: SCALE StatefulSet to 0<br/>HTTPS ServiceAccount Token
        end
    end

    %% Flow 3: Metrics Collection
    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Prometheus,NotebookCtrl: Flow 3: Metrics Collection
        Prometheus->>NotebookCtrl: GET /metrics<br/>HTTP/8080
        NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: LIST StatefulSets<br/>HTTPS ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: StatefulSet list
        NotebookCtrl-->>Prometheus: Prometheus metrics<br/>HTTP Response
    end

    %% Flow 4: Notebook Restart on ConfigMap Update
    rect rgb(255, 240, 255)
        Note over User,NotebookCtrl: Flow 4: Notebook Restart on ConfigMap Update
        User->>K8sAPI: UPDATE ConfigMap<br/>HTTPS Bearer Token
        User->>K8sAPI: ANNOTATE Notebook<br/>notebooks.opendatahub.io/notebook-restart=true<br/>HTTPS Bearer Token
        K8sAPI-->>NotebookCtrl: Watch notification
        NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: DELETE Pod<br/>HTTPS ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI-->>StatefulSet: Pod deleted
        Note over StatefulSet: StatefulSet Controller<br/>recreates Pod
        NotebookCtrl->>K8sAPI: REMOVE restart annotation<br/>HTTPS ServiceAccount Token
    end
